{{Top|leg}}
'''Arsensalts''' referred to a [[Mineral/Legends|mineral]] concoction that was developed by the [[New Jedi Order]] for use as a countermeasure against [[blorash jelly]], a particularly effective biot utilized by [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Warrior caste|Warriors]]. It literally dissolved the living gelatin, freeing the victim from its grasp.

